<p>I have a problem using two joins in one query. While this query returns nothing:</p>  <pre><code>q={!join+from=a+to=b}text_stem_ascii:(text)^5 OR {!join+from=a+to=b}text:(text)^10 </code></pre>  <p>the following query (please note the missing joins) returns something:</p>  <pre><code>q=text_stem_ascii:(text)^5 OR text:(text)^10 </code></pre>  <p>the fields <code>text</code> and <code>text_stem_ascii</code> always contain some data so it's not an issue of missing data.</p>